<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Echo - Cart</title>
    <meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport">
    <meta content="Free HTML Templates" name="keywords">
    <meta content="Free HTML Templates" name="description">

    <!-- Favicon -->
    <link href="img/favicon.ico" rel="icon">

    <!-- Google Web Fonts -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <!-- Font Awesome -->
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.10.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-rbsA2VBKQhggwzxH7pPCaAqO46MgnOM80zW1RWuH61DGLwZJEdK2Kadq2F9CUG65" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <!-- Libraries Stylesheet -->
    <link href="lib/animate/animate.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="lib/owlcarousel/assets/owl.carousel.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    

    <!-- Customized Bootstrap Stylesheet -->
    <link href="/stylesheets/style.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">

    <link href='https://unpkg.com/boxicons@2.1.2/css/boxicons.min.css' rel='stylesheet'>
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.6.0/jquery.min.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
    <!-- Topbar Start -->
    <div class="container-fluid">
        <div class="row bg-secondary  px-xl-5 row px-xl-5">

            <div class="col-lg-6  text-center text-lg-right ">
                <% if (user) { %>
                    <div class="d-inline-flex align-items-center d-block d-lg-none">

                        <a href="/wishlist" class="btn px-0 ml-2">
                            <i class="fas fa-heart text-dark"></i>
                            <% if(listCount){ %>
                                <span class="badge text-dark border border-dark rounded-circle"
                                    style="padding-bottom: 2px;">
                                    <%= listCount%>
                                </span>
                                <% } %>
                        </a>

                        <a href="/cart" class="btn px-0 ml-2">
                            <i class="fas fa-shopping-cart text-dark"></i>
                            <% if(cartCount){ %>
                                <span class="badge text-dark border border-dark rounded-circle" id="cartCount"
                                    style="padding-bottom: 2px;">
                                    <%= cartCount%>
                                </span>
                                <% } %>
                        </a>
                        <div class="btn-group ml-5">
                            <button type="button"
                                class="btn btn-sm rounded-pill btn-light dropdown-toggle text-uppercase"
                                style="font-weight: bold;" data-toggle="dropdown">
                                <%= user.userName %> <i class="fa fa-user"></i>
                            </button>
                            <div class="dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-right">
                                <a href="/profile" class="dropdown-item" type="button">My Profile <i
                                        class="fa fa-user"></i></a>
                                <a href="/logout" class="dropdown-item btn btn-danger " type="button">Logout</a>

                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <% }else{ %>
                        <div class="d-inline-flex  d-block d-lg-none float-right mt-3 mb-2">
                            <div class="float-right">
                                <a href="/login"> <button type="button"
                                        class="btn btn-sm btn-success float-right rounded">Login</button></a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <% } %>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row align-items-center bg-light py-3 px-xl-5 d-none d-lg-flex "
            style="background-image:url('https://wallpapers.com/images/featured/black-wuuaobghtdllhliu.webp') ;">
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-12">
                <a href="" class="text-decoration-none">
                    <span class="h1 text-uppercase text-primary  px-2 rounded" style="color: black;">Echo</span>
                    <span class="h1 text-uppercase  bg-primary px-2 ml-n1 rounded" style="color: black;">Cart</span>
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-6 text-left">
                <form action="/search" method="post">
                    <div class="input-group">
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Search for products" name="search">
                        <div class="input-group-append">
                            <button type="submit" class="bg-transparent">
                                <span class="input-group-text bg-transparent text-primary">
                                    <i class="fa fa-search"></i>
                                </span>
                            </button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-6 text-right">
                <% if (user) { %>
                    <div class="btn-group">
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm rounded-pill btn-light dropdown-toggle text-uppercase"
                            style="font-weight: bold;" data-toggle="dropdown">
                            <%= user.userName %> <i class="fa fa-user"></i>
                        </button>
                        <div class="dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-right">
                            <a href="/profile" class="dropdown-item" type="button">My Profile <i
                                    class="fa fa-user"></i></a>
                            <a href="/logout" class="dropdown-item btn btn-danger " type="button">Logout</a>

                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <%} else { %>

                        <a href="/login"> <button type="button"
                                class="btn btn-sm btn-success rounded">Login</button></a>
                        <% } %>
            </div>


        </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Topbar End -->


    <!-- Navbar Start -->
    <div class="container-fluid bg-secondary mb-30">
        <div class="row px-xl-5">
            <div class="col-lg-3 d-none d-lg-block">
                <a class="btn d-flex align-items-center justify-content-between bg-primary w-100" data-toggle="collapse"
                    href="#navbar-vertical" style="height: 65px; padding: 0 30px;">
                    <h6 class="text-dark m-0"><i class="fa fa-bars mr-2"></i>Categories</h6>
                    <i class="fa fa-angle-down text-dark"></i>
                </a>
                <nav class="collapse position-absolute navbar navbar-vertical navbar-light align-items-start p-0 bg-light"
                    id="navbar-vertical" style="width: calc(100% - 30px); z-index: 999;">
                    <div class="navbar-nav w-100">

                        <% allCategory.forEach((Cat)=>{ %>
                            <a href="/productCategory/<%= Cat._id %>" class="nav-item nav-link">
                                <%= Cat.category %>
                            </a>
                            <% }) %>

                    </div>
                </nav>
            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-9">
                <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg bg-dark navbar-dark py-3 py-lg-0 px-0 ">

                    <button type="button" class="navbar-toggler ml-3" data-toggle="collapse"
                        data-target="#navbarCollapse">
                        <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
                    </button>
                    <a href="" class="text-decoration-none d-block d-lg-none">
                        <span class="h1 text-uppercase text-primary  px-2 rounded" style="color: black;">Echo</span>
                        <span class="h1 text-uppercase  bg-primary px-2 ml-n1 rounded mr-5"
                            style="color: black;">Cart</span>
                    </a>

                    <div class="collapse navbar-collapse justify-content-between" id="navbarCollapse">
                        <div class="navbar-nav mr-auto py-0 ml-3">
                            <a href="/" class="nav-item nav-link active">Home</a>
                            <a href="/shopping" class="nav-item nav-link">Shop</a>


                            <a href="" class="nav-item nav-link" class="btn btn-primary" data-toggle="modal"
                                data-target="#exampleModalLong">About Us</a>
                        </div>
                        <% if (user) { %>
                            <div class="navbar-nav ml-auto py-0 d-none d-lg-block ">
                                <a href="/wishlist" class="btn px-0 mr-3">
                                    <i class="fas fa-heart text-primary"></i>
                                    <% if(listCount){ %>
                                        <span class="badge text-secondary border border-secondary rounded-circle"
                                            style="padding-bottom: 2px;">
                                            <%= listCount%>
                                        </span>
                                        <% } %>
                                </a>

                                <a href="/cart" class="btn px-0 mr-5">
                                    <i class="fas fa-shopping-cart text-primary"></i>
                                    <% if(cartCount){ %>

                                        <span class="badge text-secondary border border-secondary rounded-circle "
                                            id="cartCount" style="padding-bottom: 2px; ">
                                            <%= cartCount %>
                                        </span>
                                        <% } %>
                                </a>
                            </div>
                            <% } %>

                    </div>
                </nav>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>



    <!-- Button trigger modal -->


    <!-- Modal -->
    <div class="modal fade" id="exampleModalLong" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="exampleModalLongTitle"
        aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
            <div class="align-items-center modal-content">
                <div class="modal-header">
                    <h5 class="modal-title text-warning" id="exampleModalLongTitle">About Us</h5>

                    </button>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <h6 class="align-items-center">We’re so Glad you’re here! Either you loved us and wished to know
                        more about us. Or maybe you happen to be lost. Anyway you came till here, then let’s get to know
                        each other a little better?

                        Trust us, we won’t bore you out.
                        <h6>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <p>
                        Echo Cart, we’re a family of Common Minded Youngsters who love to create Uncommon Designs on
                        everyday fashion. There’s no limit for the products and works we wish to do, we’ll go for
                        whatever we can get our hands on. P.S: We are all Verum Malayalis from the God’s Own Country,
                        Kerala!.</p>

                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <p>
                        We’re a Team, OOPS Sorry! A Family of Young Designers. And Theoretically, Echo Cart is a
                        hardworking and Self-Governing Online Brand which manufactures own products and sell it directly
                        to the customer without any third party agents to ensure Best-Standard Quality and Pricing. We
                        don’t have any Large-Scale Funding or Multi-level Corporations behind us, just the hard work and
                        small-scale savings of a few passionate youngsters. We make designs on anything under the sky
                        from even a Vaazha to Kandaka Shani!
                        Please feel free to reach to us for any assistance Guys. We’d love to interact with you anytime!
                        We have our Head Office at Calicat, Kerala and an own production unit in Banglore , Karnataka.
